		| Header C	| Item C 1	|
		
		Then the headings will be "Header A" and "Header B" and "Header C"
		And the item for "Header A" will be "Item A 1"
		And the item for "Header B" will be "Item B 1"
		And the item for "Header C" will be "Item C 1"
	
